query:
SELECT cmlNumber, nominalThickness, previousThickness, tActual, tml1 
FROM tmlReadings 
WHERE inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber LIKE '%54-11-001%')
AND cmlNumber IN ('3', '7', '8', '9', '1', '2')
ORDER BY CAST(cmlNumber AS UNSIGNED);
